formulas.name: f_ResidentCoordinatorWillText
formulas.expression:
"

(1) Assist " & {!Contact.Full_Name__c} & " and household members in understanding the lease terms and property rules before he/she moves in, and answer any questions they may have about their tenant rights and responsibilities after move-in.

" & BR() & "

(2) Provide information and advice to client and household members to assist them with any short-term budgeting challenges they may face, to support them in paying the rent on time and avoiding late charges or lease violations.

" & BR() & "

(3) Develop a plan with client and household members to address any barriers they may face in meeting their rental obligations.

" & BR() & "

(4) Have a weekly check-in with either client and household members to learn of any questions or problems they are having at the property.

" & BR() & "

(5) Advise client and household members on how to prepare for a successful inspection of their unit and advise them on any follow-up required by the property manager.

" & BR() & "

(6) Advise client and household members on how to prepare for their annual re-certification of eligibility for the property and advise them on any follow-up required by the property manager.

" & BR() & "

(7) Advise and support client and household members in requesting and receiving needed maintenance at their unit in areas that are the responsibility of the property manager.

" & BR() & "

(8) Advise and support client and household members in pursuing any requests for reasonable accommodations that may be needed because of client's disability.

" & BR() & "

(9) Advise and support client and household members in responding to any complaints they receive from neighbors or any complaints they would like to make about their neighbors.

" & BR() & "

(10) Meet regularly with the " & TEXT({!Contact.Partner_Property__c}) & " property manager to identify well in advance of a lease violation notice any problems or concerns of the property manager with respect to client and household members' lease compliance.

" & BR() & "

(11) Organize and invite client and household members to Housing Choices sponsored events designed to promote a positive, inclusive, and supportive living environment at " & TEXT({!Contact.Partner_Property__c}) & ".

" & BR() & "

(12) Provide other assistance as may be needed to help the household achieve their goals of establishing a positive rental history and creating a satisfying home environment at " & TEXT({!Contact.Partner_Property__c}) & " Apartments.

"
